4
5
6
</pre></td><td class="rouge-code"><pre><span class="nt">font-weight</span><span class="err">：</span><span class="nt">bold</span><span class="o">;</span>
<span class="nt">单词取值</span><span class="err">：</span>
<span class="nt">bold</span><span class="err">：</span><span class="nt">加粗</span>
<span class="nt">bolder</span><span class="err">：</span><span class="nt">更粗</span>
<span class="nt">lighter</span><span class="err">：</span><span class="nt">细线</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="nt">默认</span><span class="o">)</span>
<span class="nt">数字取值</span><span class="err">：100</span><span class="o">~</span><span class="err">900</span><span class="nt">之间整百</span>
</pre></td></tr></tbody></table></code></pre></div></div>
