</pre></td><td class="rouge-code"><pre><span class="nt">color</span><span class="err">：</span><span class="nt">值</span><span class="o">;</span>
<span class="nt">值样式</span><span class="err">：</span><span class="nt">颜色单词</span><span class="err">、</span><span class="nt">rgb</span><span class="err">、</span><span class="nt">rgba</span><span class="err">、</span><span class="nf">#FF0000</span><span class="err">、</span><span class="nf">#F00</span>
<span class="nt">常用灰色</span><span class="err">：</span><span class="nt">三原色的值都相同</span><span class="err">，</span><span class="nt">就是灰色</span><span class="err">，</span><span class="nt">值越小</span><span class="err">，</span><span class="nt">越黑色</span><span class="err">，</span><span class="nt">值越大</span><span class="err">，</span><span class="nt">越白色</span>
</pre></td></tr></tbody></table></code></pre></div></div>
